comments: Harris (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position on Doncic (DAL) during the drive.  He places an arm against his side and when he swipes down he avoids making any contact.
Jokic (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Doncic (DAL).
Jokic (DEN) is in the lane for less than three seconds and becomes imminently legal when Doncic (DAL) drives to the rim.
Cauley-Stein (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Jokic (DEN).
Multiple angles were reviewed. Jokic (DEN) swipes down toward the ball. There is no clear and conclusive video angle that shows contact with Finney-Smith (DAL).
Milsap (DEN) makes contact with Kleber?s (DAL) off arm before he starts his upward shooting motion and does not affect his SQBR.
During the rebound, Jokic (DEN) and Cauley-Stein (DAL) engage and disengage.
Finney-Smith (DAL) makes marginal contact with Jokic (DEN), whose reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Murray (DEN) is in a legal position in Richardson's (DAL) path, who turns and rolls into Murray, without delivering contact.
Jokic (DEN) cleanly deflects the pass away from Cauley-Stein (DAL).
Richardson (DAL) makes marginal contact with Jokic (DEN) prior to the pass.
Richardson (DAL) briefly grasps and releases Jokic's (DEN) jersey, and does not affect his FOM.
Jokic (DEN) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Cauley-Stein (DAL) tries to steal the ball and marginal contact occurs to Jokic's (DEN) arm.
During the screen, Cauley-Stein (DAL) and Jokic (DEN) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Harris (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Cauley-Stein's (DAL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Murray (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Richardson (DAL).

Finney-Smith (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Barton (DEN). Barton fumbles the ball and legally recovers it prior to starting his upward shooting motion, gathering on his right foot and then jumping off his left.
Doncic (DAL) maintains space with a forearm at the start and end of his drive without extending it into Barton (DEN).

Jokic (DEN) is in Richardson's (DAL) path before the contact on the dribble hand-off. After the initial contact, Jokic moves off the screen and Richardson changes direction along with Murray (DEN), back into Jokic, who is in his path.
At the start of the drive, Richardson (DAL) places a hand/arm to Jokic's (DEN) front that affects his SQBR.  The illegal contact by Richardson precedes any contact delivered by Jokic.
During the drive, Kleber (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position on Dozier (DEN).
Finney-Smith (DAL) makes incidental contact with Jokic (DEN) as he cleanly deflects the pass away.
Barton (DEN) cleanly dislodges the ball from Cauley-Stein (DAL) during his driving shot attempt.  Any contact to Cauley-Stein's hand/arm after the ball is dislodged is deemed incidental.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Harris (DEN) reaches for the ball and makes marginal contact with Doncic's (DAL) arm without affecting his ability to control the ball.
Cauley-Stein (DAL) makes foot to foot contact with Murray (DEN) when he returns to the floor from his jump shot attempt.
Dozier (DEN) jumps and reaches for the ball and any contact with Kleber (DAL) as he secures the rebound is incidental.
Dozier (DEN) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
Cauley-Stein (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Jokic (DEN).
